run above command for the dependency
Initialize Prisma (Postgres)

In your apps/api folder:

Run npx prisma init.

Update the DATABASE_URL in your .env file: DATABASE_URL="postgresql://dev_user:dev_password@localhost:5432/underwriting_core?schema=public"

B. Initialize Mongoose (MongoDB)

Add this to your .env in apps/api: MONGO_URL="mongodb://localhost:27017/underwriting_medical"

C. Install the Kafka Client

We will use kafkajs for our event-driven logic: npm install kafkajs
